snippet.title: E3 2009: Developer Walkthrough
snippet.description:
"Learn the ropes in the rookie training grounds."

Originally known as Zephyr: Rise of The Elementals, this developer walkthrough will show you how to complete the first zone in the demo. Can you find all the differences?
